<div id="container">
	<!-- <img id="background" src={background.src} alt="" fetchpriority="high" /> -->
	<main>
		<section id="hero">
			<h1>Woosik Koong</h1>
			<h2>Software Engineer based in Philadelphia <span id="amp">;</span></h2>
			<section>
				<p>Hello! I’m a software engineer with most of my experience in <b>web development</b>. I transitioned into software engineering in 2017 after studying Economics and working as a project manager. The transition was both challenging and exciting. Coming from a non-technical background, everything felt new and full of possibility. </p>	
				<p>The first phase of my career was spent constantly learning frontend web technologies, with a primary focus on writing clean, maintainable code in <b>JavaScript and React</b>. It’s been fascinating to watch the frontend landscape evolve over the years, and it’s still remarkable to see how quickly the software engineering field shifts—especially with the advent of AI.</p>
				<p>As I’ve grown as an engineer, I’ve started thinking more about the bigger picture—reflecting on the trade-offs behind my decisions. I’ve realized there’s no single right answer, only <b>trade-offs</b>. With the ever-fast-changing landscape of technology, I’m excited about the ideas I’ll be able to bring to life in the future!</p>
				<p>Outside of work, I’m always daydreaming about how to perfect my <b>jump shot</b>.</p>
			</section>
		</section>
	</main>
</div>

<style>
	:root {
		--black: #252525;
		--gray: #6b6b6b; 
		--green: #24d05a;
		--blue: #10a2f5;
		--red: #E81828;
	}

	#background {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		z-index: -1;
		filter: blur(100px);
	}

	#container {
		color: var(--black);
		font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Arial Nova', 'Nimbus Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
		height: 100%;
		
	}

	main {
		height: 100%;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	section {
		z-index: 2;
	}

	#hero {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-end;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 2rem 1rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 22px;
		margin-top: 0.25em;
	}

	#links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 16px;
	}

	#links a {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 10px 12px;
		color: #111827;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	#links a:hover {
		color: rgb(78, 80, 86);
	}

	#links a svg {
		height: 1em;
		margin-left: 8px;
	}

	#links a.button {
		color: white;
		background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #3245ff 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
		box-shadow:
			inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12),
			inset 0 -2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
		border-radius: 10px;
	}

	#links a.button:hover {
		color: rgb(230, 230, 230);
		box-shadow: none;
	}

	pre {
		font-family:
			ui-monospace, 'Cascadia Code', 'Source Code Pro', Menlo, Consolas, 'DejaVu Sans Mono',
			monospace;
		font-weight: normal;
		background: linear-gradient(14deg, #d83333 0%, #f041ff 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		margin: 0;
	}

	h1 {
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin-bottom: 4px;
	}

	h2 {
		margin: 0 0 1em;
		font-weight: normal;
		color: var(--gray);
		font-size: 18px;
	}

	p {
		color: #4b5563;
		font-size: 16px;
		line-height: 24px;
		letter-spacing: -0.006em;
		margin: 1.5rem 0;
		max-width: 600px;
		text-align: justify;
	}

	code {
		display: inline-block;
		background:
			linear-gradient(66.77deg, #f3cddd 0%, #f5cee7 100%) padding-box,
			linear-gradient(155deg, #d83333 0%, #f041ff 18%, #f5cee7 45%) border-box;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border: 1px solid transparent;
		padding: 6px 8px;
	}

	#amp {
		font-weight: bold;
		color: var(--green);
	}

	.box {
		padding: 16px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 1px solid white;
	}

	#news {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 16px;
		right: 16px;
		max-width: 300px;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: background 0.2s;
		backdrop-filter: blur(50px);
	}

	#news:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
	}

	@media screen and (max-height: 368px) {
		#news {
			display: none;
		}
	}

	@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
		#container {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		#hero {
			display: block;
			padding-top: 10%;
		}

		#links {
			flex-wrap: wrap;
		}

		#links a.button {
			padding: 14px 18px;
		}

		#news {
			right: 16px;
			left: 16px;
			bottom: 2.5rem;
			max-width: 100%;
		}
	}
</style>
